// Solution of 10 Days of Statistics challenge on HackerRank
// Day 4: Geometric Distribution II
// Found at https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/s10-geometric-distribution-2/problem?isFullScreen=true
// --------------------------------------------------------------

p = 1/3

print(round(sum((1 - p) ** (n - 1) * p for n in range(1, 6)), 3))